Commment: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是转学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是位漂亮的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有人忘了盯着别人看是很失礼的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安  骑士君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:22.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（学院内某方面较活跃的学生会被周围冠以「君」等称号）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让你受到惊扰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经参观完学校了吗？妃宫千早同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么你会知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梶浦老师告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是3年级C班的七七原薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是同一个班  还有宿舍也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七原同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我薰子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  我带你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:03:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一般都不会称呼学校为「圣应女学院」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是直接说「我们这」或者「圣应」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟其它学校不大一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  我还不够了解这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么说的  形容跟周围啊社会脱节了的那话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超然脱俗」…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有人说这里是「温室」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概好坏两方面的意思都有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在上课铃声响起前就位做好上课的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们忘了吗  七七原薰子同学  妃宫千早同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  梶浦老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妃宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  能适应吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你的妈妈也让我一定要照顾好你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不必客气有什么事就来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方首先要将俗语和术语挑明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后不要把助词弄错…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都要在8日前将第二章翻译后提交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的课就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:04:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的父母是外国人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只不过外婆是北欧人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  抱歉  因为你太擅长英语所以我以为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算不上擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过我不知道除了学习之外还有什么事可以打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人羡慕  作业竟然要翻译第二章一整章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意的话  我来教你做如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天放学后有时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  在邀请她约会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织理  喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开我玩笑啦  我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  薰子  作业是要自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织理啊  你这不是听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪薰子你的声音太欢悦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是神近香织理同学  跟我们一样是住校生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  是妃宫千早同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在转学的第一天就传遍整个学院了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年级才转学来的确是挺稀奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还这么一头银发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织理  不要再逗千早了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子才刚认识就对人家一见倾心  真让我不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织理真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回宿舍去了吧  我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常纤细  如雾一般的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没多远  跑回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优雨  快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都湿了啊  会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使…大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  快醒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话身体会受寒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从宿舍叫初音过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还是直接带她回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力气挺大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她…优雨看起来很轻的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优雨你怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体的事你自己最清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶紧暖暖身才行  要不要喝点汤？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  总之先回房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  这还真是让初音姐姐担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优雨今天早上也没吃早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上也？那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼了  我叫宫藤阳向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妃宫千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳向  请问要借用厨房的话需要跟谁申请？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  并不需要许可的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优雨  不吃点东西的话对身体不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身子还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有胃口的话来一起尝一下甜点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}　Eton Mess{\r}\N是伊顿麦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由英国伊顿公学发祥的甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将草莓  奶油还有烤好的焗蛋泡戳碎搅拌后再品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要茶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢你  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久没能跟那孩子相处得那么开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的事  我只是给你们送甜点过去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优雨竟然要再来一杯  这种事从没发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  你又犯平时的坏习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子也感冒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦  完全不是那么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是犯了平时的坏习惯被美女迷住了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…香织理！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得千早好厉害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转眼就能做出甜点等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美的女性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  已经被迷得无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织理！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来真的是发烧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连初音都这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让薰子这样的人夸奖  我非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在圣应有着低年级学生要作为妹妹服侍高年级学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高年级学生要做为姐姐教育引导低年级学生的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  史将成为千早大人的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家时一直是以侍女的身份服侍您的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边也将一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做好准备了  请动身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住校生们都已入浴完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心有其他人会进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的女性…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想颓废到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你要不要转去圣应试试？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的话都是些贤淑的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很适合千早相处的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  妈妈  问题不是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托梶浦绯纱子小姐就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟她是学院长代理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早这么可爱一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  不是这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是女学院  而我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史…史？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来给您擦背了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给史吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史的使命是用尽一切力量  让千早大人能平稳度过学院生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是史是女孩子啊  这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连史这种程度的身体都让您受惊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此以后要在圣应生活是非常困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让千早大人适应女性身体才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为以触觉刺激也是非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部  胸部压着我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史  你用不着做到这种地步啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:29.57,title0,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}身为少女的日子与危机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栀子花的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭  这并不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  快离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让其他人看见你在流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看起来美丽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连招呼也不打一下吗  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以去证实流言是真实的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  我并没有这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你跟其他人略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此  我自己也够与众不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织理…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他人怎么说  我都会诚实地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你问香织理？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个怎样的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说  我挺喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然毒舌和喜欢捉弄人这点让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她却是个大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是同感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想香织理会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道千早能认真去了解她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟她有着不少流言蜚语
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来  千早既漂亮又能干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一颗为人着想的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子才是直率而容易相处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  继续复习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善良…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  想家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织理…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得肯定没那么容易蒙混过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这就投降了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要公布于众我也无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如香织理你想那么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是放得开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我有点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是父母之命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然还真能接受这种荒唐的要求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到泡红茶我是比不上小史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以给你泡了花草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是薄红葵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅好看  还可以暖和身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次碰到你时  你显得十分警戒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你很轻松就抱起了优雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管优雨多么轻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子也不可能轻易地抱起一个女孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在女生看来你完美得甚至让人妒忌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你饰演着男人眼中最完美的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想就说得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  还有一些只有我才发觉到的细节
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也对我说过  「怎么可能」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算说出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还希望你能继续留在这所学院里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我想偷看过我跟她之间的秘密的你会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有自己的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打扰你们的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  你方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妃宫千早  今年新住进宿舍的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫凯莉·格兰塞里乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身处黑夜  掌管众多星辰的星星公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星与冥王星交织出的光谱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出你背负着奇异的命运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯莉  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我的  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关门时间快到了  请准备离开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我别人能不能看出你是男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是奉承  我实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你是一个完美的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看穿是因为我是特例
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要说千早你有什么要改正之处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要注意不要表现得过分完美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么这么问？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…只是有点担心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  史
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  千早大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始终还是不能融入这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  跟我来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我赢了  千早就要向我坦白一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先取得有效击中的人胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间分出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}En garde{\r}\N各就位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}Prêts{\r}\N准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我先确认一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时的我  想必显得十分滑稽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:19:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么  你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早你究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也许你无法相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我除此别无选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而事到如今  我会离开这里  离开圣应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样就能解决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是以这种被摇摆不定的心意欺骗着我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  所以我要用我的办法试探你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}Allez{\r}\N开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这点水平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种摇摆不定的心意欺骗我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连累了香织理  究竟想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}Halte{\r}\N胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是觉得不可饶恕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我也稍微冷静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织理倒是为什么放他一马？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是伪装印象战术
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替千早保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为代价让他成为我在学院里的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么薰子要对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你现在离开优雨她们一定会伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…我也挺崇拜你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外你又跟我的姐姐有点相似
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点让我觉得有点生气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我希望你继续留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早大人  请擦眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭什么  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是喜极而泣吧  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来一年可以随心所欲地看女生换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是出人意外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几天这么快就被两个人发现了真相
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还能继续留在学院里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史都隐约觉得这是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.87,0:22:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前体育课换衣服的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿内衣的样子！
