Dialogue: 1,0:23:47.13,0:23:53.21,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}纵若悲伤  奏响当下
Dialogue: 1,0:23:53.36,0:24:01.69,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}拥抱真爱  向往未来
